org.jamsim.ascape.ui.cmd
Class SingleVariableCommand

java.lang.Object
  org.jamsim.ascape.ui.cmd.SingleVariableCommand
All Implemented Interfaces:
ScapeRCommand, RUICommand
public class SingleVariableCommand
extends java.lang.Object
implements ScapeRCommand

An R command that takes the name of a single variable and displays a table. Provides a RObjectTreeBuilder for the user to select the variable.

$Revision: 183 $

Constant Field Values

REPLACEMENT

public static final java.lang.String REPLACEMENT
Replacement string. Before executed on the supplied command, the commmand text is searched for this value and it is replaced with the single variable selected in the displayed RObjectTreeBuilder.

See Also:
Constant Field Values
Constructor Detail

SingleVariableCommand

public SingleVariableCommand(java.lang.String name,
                             java.lang.String variableTypes,
                             java.lang.String cmdText)
Default constructor.

Parameters:
name - name of command
variableTypes - The types of variable class this command works on. eg: "list,data.frame,integer" separated by comma (NB do not include a space after the comma). Use null to work on all objects. The RObjectTreeBuilder will only display objects of these types.
cmdText - the command executed in R. Before executed REPLACEMENT is replaced with the single variable selected in the displayed RObjectTreeBuilder
